HIGHLY EXPERIMENTAL SOFTWARE

	ZK - SPACE

HOW TO TEST IT:

requirements:
1. tendermint@v0.34.24
2. go compiler


instructions:

1. download and unzip this folder
2. download the tendermint executable and place it in the folder
3. install go
4. run go get ./...
5. run go build
6. chmod +x *
7. run ./run.sh

